- fD (Martin et al. 2015) can be applied on small genomics regions to detect introgression
- Inference of selection can be difficult as adaptive introgression can lead to different patterns than traditional hard sweep
- inference of selection only give indirect evidence
- adaptive introgression should be ultimately validated by fitness advantage (linked to markers function with phenotype-genotype associations)},
